 to a less-than-or-equals:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
T_{\beta}^{\le}(x)=\begin{cases}
\beta x & \mbox{ for }0\le x\le\frac{1}{2}\\
\beta\left(x-\frac{1}{2}\right) & \mbox{ for }\frac{1}{2}<x\le1
