 A zero-free ray extends along the positive real axis.
 These rings have a radius of approximately 
\begin_inset Formula $\left|z\right|\approx35,55,100,190,350$
\end_inset

 with these figures good to about one-and-a-half digits.
 The rings are wide, and have structure.
